27:13.382 --> 27:14.963
That house is on the list.

27:15.051 --> 27:19.420
Look, there's nothing wrong with that house
that a carpenter and a little paint can't cure.

27:19.514 --> 27:23.382
If I can contact the owner, he or she can file
an objection to stop the demolition.

27:23.476 --> 27:26.968
But they only got 30 days to do it from the day
they post the legal notice.

27:27.063 --> 27:28.303
What's in it for you?

27:28.397 --> 27:30.809
-Not a damn thing.
-Then why are you bothering?

27:30.900 --> 27:33.482
My mother's house got done the same way
they're gonna do this one.

27:34.403 --> 27:35.654
You know how I can reach your neighbors?

27:35.738 --> 27:38.480
They're having some difficulty now,
but they're trying to get home.

27:38.574 --> 27:40.405
Will you give me
their number so I can talk to them?

27:41.452 --> 27:44.660
Give me yours.
If they wanna call you, they will.

27:44.747 --> 27:46.578
Fair enough.

27:48.876 --> 27:49.831
(HlSSlNG)

27:49.919 --> 27:51.659
MAN ON P.A.:
These guys have a very particular metabolism

27:51.754 --> 27:54.917
that requires them to warm up,
eat a whole lot,

27:55.007 --> 27:58.124
and then they can chase down things,
but only for a short distance.

27:58.219 --> 27:59.800
They're much more adept at catching things...

27:59.887 --> 28:01.752
Quite a spectacle.

28:01.973 --> 28:06.137
Reminds me of a Louisiana State
highway contract being left for bid.

28:07.103 --> 28:08.718
This is more dignified.

28:08.813 --> 28:10.678
Why'd you pick this spot?

28:10.773 --> 28:13.765
JAMES: lfl brought you into the field office,
I'd have to file a 302.

28:14.527 --> 28:17.769
You know an NOPD
Lieutenant Terrence Colson?

28:17.947 --> 28:20.108
Colson. I know the name.

28:22.243 --> 28:24.029
Whatever it is, you don't seem happy about it.

28:24.120 --> 28:27.283
About a year ago, he comes to my office

28:27.373 --> 28:30.661
asking for two shell casings
I had in my possession.

28:31.669 --> 28:33.705
They were connected
to a murder in the lberville

28:33.796 --> 28:36.378
after the storm, a man named Seals.

28:36.465 --> 28:39.957
How I got the casings
is a long story, but Terry...

28:41.971 --> 28:44.713
Colson finds out l have the casings

28:44.807 --> 28:46.718
and he comes to collect them for evidence.

28:46.809 --> 28:49.095
I don't trust the NOPD with the evidence.

28:49.645 --> 28:52.261
But he signs a receipt for them,
which I still have.

28:52.356 --> 28:56.565
-Go on.
-A few weeks ago, I got a cityjudge

28:56.652 --> 28:59.519
to release the Abreu and Seals files to me.

28:59.614 --> 29:01.650
And in them, that,

29:02.325 --> 29:05.112
which tells me one thing and one thing only...

29:07.163 --> 29:10.371
