the evidence gone missing.

30:10.643 --> 30:12.179
And so he runs a little test.

30:12.269 --> 30:14.009
And guess what?

30:14.105 --> 30:16.812
One of your shells never got to Jeff Parish.

30:17.817 --> 30:20.604
And so he knows what he's dealing with.

30:20.695 --> 30:24.404
-How do you know all that?
-He told me a year ago.

30:24.573 --> 30:26.609
