32:03.547 --> 32:05.003
NOPD, too.

32:05.424 --> 32:07.961
If it comes to it,
they'll make this guy look like Willie Horton.

32:08.052 --> 32:11.089
Stupid play, though.
Glover's history is easily verified.

32:11.180 --> 32:12.590
