32:12.681 --> 32:17.471
There is a Henry Glover down here,
a live one with a full rap sheet.

32:17.561 --> 32:20.348
So if and when they get
called on their bullshit,

32:20.439 --> 32:22.976
they'll just back up and say
they got the wrong guy.

32:23.067 --> 32:24.898
